item.title: GRAB
item.description: score:128 Chances: Grab Holdings Limited has achieved success in the field of e-wallets, food distribution, mobile and financial services in Southeast Asia. The company’s superapp model allows access to millions of users for a wide range of services, including food delivery, parcel delivery, transportation, and financial services.
